CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777370785
OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FSpeaker of the House, Sir Lindsay
OL,8,FHoyle, on Monday granted permission
OL,9,Ffor the debate and vote to take place,
OL,10,Ffollowing requests from Tory leader
OL,11,FKemi Badenoch and other senior MPs.
OL,13,FMPs will decide whether the prime
OL,14,Fminister should be referred to the
OL,15,FPrivileges Committee and investigated
OL,16,Ffor allegedly misleading parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
