PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777370785
OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FThe Privileges Committee was
OL,8,Fresponsible for ending Boris Johnson's
OL,9,Fpolitical career after it investigated
OL,10,Fhim for misleading the House over the
OL,11,F"partygate" breaches of Covid-19 laws
OL,12,Fin Downing Street.
OL,14,FHe quit as an MP in 2023 before the
OL,15,Fcommittee published a report
OL,16,Frecommending his suspension.
OL,18,FFormer Labour prime minister Gordon
OL,19,FBrown was among those to get behind
OL,20,FStarmer late on Monday night.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
