OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FAllies of the prime minister appeared
OL,8,Fconfident that a mass rebellion was
OL,9,Foff the cards as he told a packed
OL,10,Fmeeting of the Parliamentary Labour
OL,11,FParty (PLP): "When we stick together
OL,12,Fand fight together we are so much
OL,13,Fstronger."
OL,15,FStarmer sought to dismiss the Commons
OL,16,Fbid to refer him to the committee as a
OL,17,F"stunt" by political opponents intent
OL,18,Fon inflicting damage before the May
OL,19,Felections.
OL,26,@sD@NOUuD@JO]yD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
