OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FLast week, Barton's successor, Sir
OL,13,FOlly Robbins, gave evidence to the
OL,14,Fsame committee in which he described
OL,15,Fan atmosphere of "constant pressure"
OL,16,Fas his office sought to clear
OL,17,FMandelson's appointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777370785
OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FRobbins told MPs "my office and the
OL,8,FForeign Secretary's office were under
OL,9,Fconstant pressure" about the
OL,10,Fappointment in January 2025, after it
OL,11,Fhad been announced but before the
OL,12,Fsecurity checks were completed.
OL,14,FMcSweeney has been reported as one key
OL,15,Ffigure behind this pressure exerted on
OL,16,Fthe Foreign Office, with Robbins at
OL,17,Fone point being asked whether his
OL,18,Fpredecessor had received a phone call
OL,19,Ffrom the PM's then Chief of Staff
OL,20,Ftelling him to "just f*****g approve
OL,21,Fit."
OL,26,@oD@ROUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
