CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777370785
OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FStarmer has also faced questions from
OL,8,FMPs, telling them "no pressure existed
OL,9,Fwhatsoever in relation to this case".
OL,11,FIt is this apparently contradictory
OL,12,Fclaim that forms one of the reasons
OL,13,FMPs are seeking to refer him to the
OL,14,FPrivileges Committee for misleading
OL,15,Fparliament.
OL,26,@pD@SOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
