OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777370785
OL,3,CStarmer faces vote on Mandelson
OL,4,Cvetting row as ex-officials due to
OL,5,Cgive evidence
OL,7,FThe prime minister will have a chance
OL,8,Fto respond to the evidence given by
OL,9,FBarton and McSweeney when he takes
OL,10,Fquestions from MPs on Wednesday in a
OL,11,Ffinal PMQs before parliament breaks
OL,12,Fahead of the local elections.
OL,14,FFurther documents relating to
OL,15,FMandelson's appointment are expected
OL,16,Fto be released after the local
OL,17,Felections as part of the ongoing
OL,18,FHumble Address.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
